Interview Answer (2–3 Marks)

Applications of Machine Learning include healthcare (disease prediction), finance (fraud detection), e-commerce (recommendation systems), social media (face recognition), natural language processing (chatbots and translation), computer vision (image recognition), autonomous vehicles, cybersecurity, manufacturing (predictive maintenance), agriculture (crop prediction), education (personalized learning), and entertainment (movie and music recommendations).

